abstract_ssm: Nick Zedd is a filmmaker, writer, actor, and artist who became the leading figure of the Cinema of Transgression Movement (1984 - 1990). The Nick Zedd Papers preserve Zedd's films and writing, which include scripts, notebooks, sketchbooks, photographs, and audio and moving image elements.
